      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/chinese-buyers-cancel-or-postpone-australian-wheat-buys-amid-global-oversupply-2024-03-14/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[直接了解交易情况的贸易消息人士称，中国小麦进口商取消或推迟了约 100 万吨澳大利亚小麦进口，因全球库存增加拖累价格。]]></description>
